msgid "Containerization and Virtualization"
msgstr ""

#: src/distro/popular-applications/containerization-and-virtualization/index.md:3
msgid ""
"This category covers container runtimes, container image tools, and other "
"virtualization-related tools."
msgstr ""

#: src/distro/popular-applications/containerization-and-virtualization/index.md:5
msgid "Container Runtimes"
msgstr ""

#: src/distro/popular-applications/containerization-and-virtualization/index.md:7
msgid "Podman"
msgstr "Podman"

#: src/distro/popular-applications/containerization-and-virtualization/index.md:9
msgid ""
"[Podman](https://docs.podman.io/en/stable/Introduction.html) is a modern, "
"daemonless container engine that provides a Docker-compatible command-line "
"interface, making it easy for users familiar with Docker to transition."
msgstr ""
"[Podman](https://docs.podman.io/en/stable/Introduction.html) 是一款現代化的無"
"守護進程容器引擎，提供與 Docker 相容的命令行介面，讓熟悉 Docker 的使用者能輕"
"鬆過渡。"

#: src/distro/popular-applications/containerization-and-virtualization/index.md:13
#: src/distro/popular-applications/containerization-and-virtualization/index.md:68
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "安裝"

#: src/distro/popular-applications/containerization-and-virtualization/index.md:15
msgid "To install Podman, add the following line to `configuration.nix`:"
msgstr "若要安裝 Podman，請將以下內容增添到 `configuration.nix`："

#: src/distro/popular-applications/containerization-and-virtualization/index.md:21
#: src/distro/popular-applications/containerization-and-virtualization/index.md:74
msgid "Verified Usage"
msgstr ""

#: src/distro/popular-applications/containerization-and-virtualization/index.md:23
msgid "`podman run`"
msgstr "`podman run`"

#: src/distro/popular-applications/containerization-and-virtualization/index.md:25
msgid "`podman run` runs a command in a new container."
msgstr "`podman run` 在新的容器中執行命令。"

#: src/distro/popular-applications/containerization-and-virtualization/index.md:28
msgid "# Start a container, execute a command, and then exit\n"
msgstr "# 啟動容器，執行命令，然後退出\n"

#: src/distro/popular-applications/containerization-and-virtualization/index.md:30
msgid "# Start a container and attach to an interactive shell\n"
msgstr "# 啟動容器並附加到互動式外殼\n"

#: src/distro/popular-applications/containerization-and-virtualization/index.md:35
msgid "`podman image`"
msgstr "`podman image`"

#: src/distro/popular-applications/containerization-and-virtualization/index.md:37
msgid "`podman image` manages local images."
msgstr "`podman image` 會管理本機映像。"

#: src/distro/popular-applications/containerization-and-virtualization/index.md:40
msgid "# List downloaded images\n"
msgstr "# 列出已下載的映像檔\n"

#: src/distro/popular-applications/containerization-and-virtualization/index.md:44
msgid "`podman ps`"
msgstr "`podman ps`"

#: src/distro/popular-applications/containerization-and-virtualization/index.md:46
msgid "`podman ps` lists containers."
msgstr "`podman ps` 列出容器。"

#: src/distro/popular-applications/containerization-and-virtualization/index.md:49
msgid "# Show the status of all containers (including exited ones)\n"
msgstr ""

#: src/distro/popular-applications/containerization-and-virtualization/index.md:53
msgid "`podman rm`"
msgstr "`podman rm`"

#: src/distro/popular-applications/containerization-and-virtualization/index.md:55
msgid "`podman rm` removes one or more containers."
msgstr "`podman rm` 移除一個或多個容器。"

#: src/distro/popular-applications/containerization-and-virtualization/index.md:58
msgid "# Remove a container named foo\n"
msgstr "# 移除名為 foo 的容器\n"

